Containers
==========

Reproducible OCI images built with Nix.


postgres-18
-----------

PostgreSQL 18, built from source, bundled with the following extensions:

  * pgactive - active-active logical replication
  * pg_rational - exact rational number type
  * timescaledb - time-series partitioning and compression
  * pgvector - vector similarity search

Available images:

  * ghcr.io/aca/containers/postgres-18:latest
  * ghcr.io/aca/containers/postgres-18:latest-amd64
  * ghcr.io/aca/containers/postgres-18:latest-arm64
